A collection of live performances, B-sides andunreleased tracks, featuring vocalist Danny Vaughan. 73:53long. The back cover art is a mock menu of a Chineserestaurant. 15 tracks: 'Forever Young' (Demo), 'Drag TheRiver' (Demo), 'Tearin Up The Night' (Demo), 'Standing Alone(Demo), 'Wait Forever' (B-side), (ALL OF THE REST ARE LIVEVERSIONS:) 'Burnin Down Inside', 'Lay Your Body Down', 'LetIt Go', 'Seasons', 'Nothin But Love', 'Shine', 'The End OfThe Summer Days', 'Get Me There', 'High' and 'Jamie'.
